		cs_bytes int,

	BEGIN

		@result = EXTRACT
			s_date DateTime,
			s_time string,
			s_sitename string,
			cs_method string,

	AS 
		SELECT * FROM 
		(
			VALUES(1,2),(2,4)
		)

	T(a, b);
